        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 29 at 6:44PM MDT until August 29 at 7:15PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>At 644 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Arlington, or
26 miles north of North La Junta, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Blue Lake and Arlington.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
